title: Egyptians vote amid complaints of repression
text:
Egyptians vote amid complaints of repression 8:45am EDT - 02:06 
Egyptians began voting on Monday in a presidential election set to deliver an easy win for incumbent Abdel Fattah al-Sisi, with turnout the main focus after all serious opposition withdrew complaining of repression. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
